name: Moo Moo's Cavalcade of Cancelled Crap
name_original: Moo Moo's Cavalcade of Cancelled Crap
description:
Various unfinished fangames that I tried to make

  • I wanna be the Bubble Bobble

My attempt to make something more  'modern' i guess. I stopped working on it because I just wasn't feeling like finishing it.

  • I WANNA BE THE ANTICHRIST

A combination of something like Burnmind and I Wanna See You Suffer. Stopped working on it for the same reasons as the last one

  • H3ppil

I honestly have no fucking idea why I made this. The least finished game out of the whole bunch.

  • I wanna bouse the Beat

A parody of I wanna beat the Bouse. I actually had fun making this one but stopped because bouse isn't really that interesting of a game to dedicate any amount of time to parodying it.

  • I wanna hate the happil / I Wanna Kill The Sauce Man!

Another parody game, this time of happil clones. I dunno why I stopped working on this one, I might remake it later down the line. My personal favorite.

-

All games contain their respective source codes.
